023/10/Liam-Noel-Gallagher@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Noel-Gallagher@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Liam-Noel-Gallagher@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺尔·加拉格尔</a>拒绝了参加即将举行的“绝对可能”巡演的机会。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/liam-gallagher-oasis-reunion-tour-noel-interview-2020-new-album-2615869">大读物 – Liam Gallagher：“绿洲团聚很快就会发生”</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">昨天（10 月 16 日）宣布了英国巡演的消息</a>，并确认 Liam 将踏上旅途，庆祝<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>首张专辑《Definitely Maybe》30 周年。</p><p>这些现场表演是这位歌手今年早些时候分享的更新的后续，他在更新中回顾了这一里程碑，并戏弄歌迷说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-next-year-for-30th-anniversary-3442321">正在寻找完整播放 1994 年专辑的方法。</a></p><p>利亚姆继续调侃这个前景，后来宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-promises-naughty-oasis-b-sides-on-definitely-maybe-tour-including-the-noel-sung-half-the-world-away-3513284">他也会演奏那个时代的“顽皮”B面歌曲</a>以及由他的兄弟、前乐队成员和绿洲乐队首席词曲作者诺埃尔演唱的《半个世界》。</p><p>然而不幸的是，对于歌迷来说，他的兄弟和前乐队成员似乎无意参加即将到来的巡演。相反，现场表演将更多地是利亚姆的个人冒险。</p><p>这条消息是在 Liam 今天（10 月 17 日）早些时候在 X（以前的 Twitter）上确认他向他的兄弟提供了参加绿洲巡演的机会，但没有任何计划实现的时候传出的。</p><p> “有人邀请他，但他拒绝了，”他在回答一位粉丝询问他何时宣布诺埃尔参与巡演时写道。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">有人邀请他，但他拒绝了</p><p>— 利亚姆·加拉格尔 (@liamgallagher) <a href="https://twitter.com/liamgallagher/status/1714196764431921350?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 10 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>为期 12 日的“绝对可能 30 年”英国和爱尔兰巡演将于 6 月 2 日在谢菲尔德拉开帷幕，然后在卡迪夫、格拉斯哥和都柏林停留。</p><p> Three dates at London&#39;s O2 venue are also planned, as are three in his hometown of Manchester, held at the Co-Op Live venue.</p><p> “I&#39;m bouncing around the house to announce the &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; Tour,” he said at the time. “The most important album of the &#39;90s bar none. I wouldn&#39;t be anywhere without it and neither would you, so let&#39;s celebrate together LG x”</p><p> It also appears that ex-Oasis guitarist Bonehead will be joining him on the tour following his solo projects and previous cancer scare – <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/oasis-bonehead-on-recent-cancer-diagnosis-its-all-clear-its-gone-3320076">he&#39;s since been given the all-clear</a> .</p><p> Tickets go on sale from 9am BST this Friday (October 20) and will be available <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fliam-gallagher-tickets%2Fartist%2F2055477" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3516470" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3516470" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3516470" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Liam and Noel Gallagher of Oasis, in 1995" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Oasis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3516470" class="wp-caption-text"> Liam and Noel Gallagher of Oasis, in 1995. CREDIT: Des Willie/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> This is far from the first time that Oasis fans have had their hopes dashed for a reunion between the brothers. In light of the 30th anniversary of &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39;, Noel confirmed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-for-2024-denies-oasis-reunion-tour-3436441">an Oasis reunion will not happening any time soon. He did, however, confirm plans for a 30th anniversary reissue of the seminal album</a> to mark the occasion.</p><p> Additionally, <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">speaking to <em>NME</em> as part of the In Conversation series</a> , Noel said that there had “never really been a serious offer about &#39;The Big O&#39; getting back together”.</p><p> Instead, the singer, songwriter and guitarist has been focusing his efforts on his <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds">High Flying Birds</a> solo project, which released their latest album <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/noel-gallaghers-high-flying-birds-council-skies-review-3450645">&#39;Council Skies&#39;</a> earlier this year and has toured throughout 2023.</p><p> Liam, on the other hand, has also been heavily involved with his own solo career and recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-announces-knebworth-live-album-and-shares-roll-it-over-video-watch-footage-preorder-3454697">released a live album</a> from <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-live-in-knebworth-kasabian-amyl-sniffers-3239799">his show at Knebworth in 2022</a> .</p><p> The event was one of his biggest headline gigs to date as a solo artist and saw him play to over 170,000 across two nights.</p><p> He has also teased that his new solo album – the follow-up to 2022&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-cmon-you-know-3231721">&#39;C&#39;Mon You Know&#39;</a> – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-hints-that-his-new-album-is-done-3499289">is now complete</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">Liam Gallagher says Noel turned down offer to take part in &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; tour</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
